# Test the coach backend from VS Code.
#
# Requires the "REST Client" extension (id: humao.rest-client).
# 1. Start the server:  cd backend && npm run dev   (or use the "backend: dev" task)
# 2. Open this file and click the "Send Request" link above any request below.
#
# To exercise the REAL Claude Haiku 4.5 generation (not the sample), put a key in
# backend/.env:  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...   then restart the server.
# Without a key the server serves the built-in sample session.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = DEV_TOKEN
@userId = demo-user

### Health check — should return { "ok": true }
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Today's session for the athlete (generated by Claude Haiku 4.5 when a key is set)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/sessions/today?user_id={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Same athlete again — must return the IDENTICAL stored session (persistence)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/sessions/today?user_id={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### A different athlete — gets its own freshly generated session
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/sessions/today?user_id=alice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Missing token — should return 401 unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/sessions/today?user_id={{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### Log what was actually done (Phase C) — feeds the NEXT day's adaptation
# To see adaptation now: POST this, then delete backend/data/sessions.json
# (keep history.json) and re-run the GET above — the new session should react.
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/sessions/log
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "session_id": "{{userId}}-2026-06-23",
  "results": [
    { "exercise": "Push-ups", "target_reps": 12, "target_hold_seconds": null, "achieved_reps": 12, "achieved_hold_seconds": null, "completed": true },
    { "exercise": "Dips", "target_reps": 8, "target_hold_seconds": null, "achieved_reps": 5, "achieved_hold_seconds": null, "completed": false },
    { "exercise": "Plank", "target_reps": null, "target_hold_seconds": 45, "achieved_reps": null, "achieved_hold_seconds": 30, "completed": false }
  ]
}
